  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      an examination of the different aspects of bariatric surgery in elderly in comparison with
      non-elderly patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      the study examines the success rate, complications, revisions, days of hospitalization and
      co-morbidities in elderly and in non-elderly patients that underwent bariatric surgery in our
      medical center
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
